===第2期===
第2期為第5-7座，全部樓高57層，除了首設264平方呎開放式戶型外，其餘單位均與第1期樓宇間隔相若<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://cms.nwd.com.hk/download/2003/36_DC3057/PDMC%20(Tai%20Wai)%20(Approved%20clean%20version%20-%2014th%20Draft_%207%20September%202020)%20with%20plans.pdf |title=柏傲莊主公契連樓宇圖則 |access-date=2020-10-14 |archive-date=2020-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015102453/https://cms.nwd.com.hk/download/2003/36_DC3057/PDMC%20(Tai%20Wai)%20(Approved%20clean%20version%20-%2014th%20Draft_%207%20September%202020)%20with%20plans.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。景觀方面，由於層數較高，除了內園及大圍區內樓景，部分東北座向高層單位更可眺望[[馬鞍山新市鎮|馬鞍山]]，而少數向南極高層單位甚至可遠眺港島[[西高山|西高山]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3bO02RmXAAE&t |title=柏傲莊T7高層景觀航拍 |access-date=2020-10-18 |archive-date=2020-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018135049/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3bO02RmXAAE&t |dead-url=no }}</ref>。項目在2020年11月7日開售，涉及337伙，反應非常理想。到月底已經累售1,347伙，佔項目約九成，套現約154億元。新世界發展執行副主席兼行政總裁[[鄭志剛|鄭志剛]]表示，項目在疫情下能夠創造佳績，反映市場對優質樓盤非常渴求。<ref>{{cite news |title=柏傲莊 II 今售315伙　累沽九成　鄭志剛﹕市場對優質盤非常渴求 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/553996/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-ii-%E4%BB%8A%E5%94%AE315%E4%BC%99-%E7%B4%AF%E6%B2%BD%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E5%BF%97%E5%89%9B-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%8D%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%B8%B4%E6%B1%82 |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=香港01 |date=2020-11-27 |archive-date=2021-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727052256/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/553996/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-ii-%E4%BB%8A%E5%94%AE315%E4%BC%99-%E7%B4%AF%E6%B2%BD%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E5%BF%97%E5%89%9B-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%8D%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%B8%B4%E6%B1%82 |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外，有一房特色戶以以1043萬元，實呎逾3萬元售出，創新界區一房呎價新高。<ref>{{cite news |title=柏傲莊II一房呎價破3萬 料創新界同類新高 |url=https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/dailyp2.php?node=1606677371192&issue=20201130 |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=明報 |date=2020-11-30}}</ref>

===第3期===
第3期由2幢住宅大樓組成（第1座和第8座），提供892伙單位，戶型涵蓋1至4房。三房和四房單位將享有開陽城門河景觀。而當中1A座樓高57層，1B座只有47層。第1A座55至61樓A室更採用大宅設計，佔地1676平方呎，附設123平方呎露台，只有7伙。第8座8至39樓採用1層12伙設計，到41至61樓主要提供佔地1200平方呎的大單位。而8B座C室提供工作間和超迷你三角形儲物室。<ref>{{cite news |title=柏傲莊III平面圖分析 4房罕見123呎大露台 3房超迷你三角形儲物室 |url=https://ps.hket.com/article/2964950/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8AIII%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9C%96%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%204%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B123%E5%91%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0%203%E6%88%BF%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E5%84%B2%E7%89%A9%E5%AE%A4?mtc=60007 |accessdate=2021-05-25 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2021-05-25 |archive-date=2021-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525040459/https://ps.hket.com/article/2964950/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8AIII%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9C%96%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%204%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B123%E5%91%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0%203%E6%88%BF%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E5%84%B2%E7%89%A9%E5%AE%A4?mtc=60007 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而所有4房2套間隔及絕大部分特色戶的客廳特設ArtiSaloon藏酒間，並備有小吧枱、[[Miele|Miele]]的咖啡機、嵌入式酒櫃、嵌入式雪櫃連冰箱及食物保溫櫃等。發展商提供3款顏色的主題飾面讓買家選擇。<ref>{{cite news |title=大圍站新盤設特色藏酒間 |url=https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/8515800-%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8d%e7%ab%99%e6%96%b0%e7%9b%a4%e8%a8%ad%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e8%97%8f%e9%85%92%e9%96%93 |accessdate=2021-05-27 |publisher=巴士的報 |date=2021-05-26 |archive-date=2021-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527113503/https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/8515800-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%99%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E8%A8%AD%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E8%97%8F%E9%85%92%E9%96%93 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而露台設L型軌道露台門，發展商正申請專利。項目將於2021年6月5日進行第一輪推售，第一輪入票數目逾2.7萬票，超額認購逾80倍，再次成為1997後票王，同時亦超越柏傲莊1、2期首輪入票數目逾兩成。<ref>{{cite news |title=柏傲莊III逾2.7萬登記 超額認購逾80倍 再膺97後票王 |url=https://ps.hket.com/article/2974417/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8AIII%E9%80%BE2.7%E8%90%AC%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%20%E8%B6%85%E9%A1%8D%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%E9%80%BE80%E5%80%8D%20%E5%86%8D%E8%86%BA97%E5%BE%8C%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%8B |accessdate=2021-06-06 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2021-06-04 |archive-date=2021-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606030859/https://ps.hket.com/article/2974417/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8AIII%E9%80%BE2.7%E8%90%AC%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%20%E8%B6%85%E9%A1%8D%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%E9%80%BE80%E5%80%8D%20%E5%86%8D%E8%86%BA97%E5%BE%8C%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%8B |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年6月30日，1A座62樓A室4房連天台特色戶，透過招標以7,650萬元售出，呎價逾4.5萬元，創新界分層式住宅呎價新紀錄。<ref>{{cite news |title=柏傲莊III四房特色戶呎售4.5萬 新界分層新高 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20210701/s00004/1625076170263/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8Aiii%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%BF%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E6%88%B6%E5%91%8E%E5%94%AE4-5%E8%90%AC-%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%88%86%E5%B1%A4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98 |accessdate=2021-07-05 |work=明報 |date=2021-07-01 |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711053109/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20210701/s00004/1625076170263/%e6%9f%8f%e5%82%b2%e8%8e%8aiii%e5%9b%9b%e6%88%bf%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e6%88%b6%e5%91%8e%e5%94%ae4-5%e8%90%ac-%e6%96%b0%e7%95%8c%e5%88%86%e5%b1%a4%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

